{"tid":1810811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MOMO公開戀愛首露面 成員保護「麥克風直接跳過」！","createTime":"2020-01-04T07:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T03:37:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24db94dc83806f202e4dc667b11f57b680569e8c","tid":1810811,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"南韓今（4日）晚間將舉辦金唱片第一天音源部門頒獎典禮，下午女團TWICE走上紅毯，也是成員MOMO爆出與Super Junior希澈戀愛之後首度露面，她以俐落直髮美翻全場，但可惜沒有發言說話，倒是子瑜受訪講了自己遵循南韓傳統，在新年喝了年糕湯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4624/d4624734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4624%2Fd4624734.jpg&h=471db28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼MOMO（上圖右）公開戀愛首露面，與成員踏上紅毯。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4624/d4624736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4624%2Fd4624736.jpg&h=0538b5f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE以裸膚色成套洋裝走上紅毯，Sana特別暗示這身服裝跟今晚表演相關。而子瑜則受訪時被問了有沒有喝年糕湯，因為南韓傳統要在元旦喝年糕湯，象徵長了一歲，她一開始說沒有，但後來似乎理解了問題才趕緊改口說，「喝了喝了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4624/d4624735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4624%2Fd4624735.jpg&h=8bb7b211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜透露自己入境隨俗，喝了新年的年糕湯。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\n不過這次踏上紅毯上只有7人，扣掉正在休養的Sana，還少了彩瑛，隊長志效解釋彩瑛現在有點不舒服，所以才無法一起走紅毯，希望大家今年都健健康康。也因為被問到今年鼠年，Sana跟定延居然在紅毯即興考志效做出「鼠年」的二行詩，脫稿演出十分親民。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4624/d4624737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4624%2Fd4624737.jpg&h=c992b56c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼成員疑似保護MOMO，受訪時麥克風直接跳過。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4624/d4624738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4624%2Fd4624738.jpg&h=10b2a7c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然而該主持人在前面訪問TWICE師妹團ITZY時，還特別讓未發言的成員對麥克風說說話，然而TWICE這回6人都有受訪，就只有MOMO沒有發言，也看得到成員傳遞麥克風時，刻意跳過MOMO，疑似想保護最近公開戀愛的她。MOMO戀情曝光首露面，也以微笑面對鏡頭，十分敬業。"},{"pid":"4321649ca398d3bcf7fccb65672bad9ba5c3c5b0","tid":1810811,"uid":208486,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扣掉正在休養的Sana</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19c5fcdae098fedc20cd0217d3dab79b0c7b7df","tid":1810811,"uid":46435,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"保護momo做咩 佢比人祝福多過比人吊wo..=="},{"pid":"50318282b0cd21da51748c604c6346c938a747dd","tid":1810811,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f19c5fcdae098fedc20cd0217d3dab79b0c7b7df","tid":1810811,"uid":46435,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"保護momo做咩 佢比人祝福多過比人吊wo..=="},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"JYP爸爸做既任何一個舉動都係保護緊佢既女兒"},{"pid":"fa16885e92c0f6adacdcc69c37f1a700ac662312","tid":1810811,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50318282b0cd21da51748c604c6346c938a747dd","tid":1810811,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f19c5fcdae098fedc20cd0217d3dab79b0c7b7df","tid":1810811,"uid":46435,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"保護momo做咩 佢比人祝福多過比人吊wo..=="},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"JYP爸爸做既任何一個舉動都係保護緊佢既女兒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"JYP真係好爸爸來..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a236fdbcd2690f980f01a594245e0b872435233e","tid":1810811,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"我和sana好熟 我地有啲關係"},{"pid":"f8919a01d167f11b417fc1b7860643be1d21141a","tid":1810811,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a236fdbcd2690f980f01a594245e0b872435233e","tid":18